en Club, Cavallo, Soktas, and Giza House brands; manufactures and sells ceramic and composite insulators for transmission and distribution lines, sub-stations, power equipment, and railway electrification industries; and engages in generating clean energy using solar, wind, hybrid, and floating solar systems. The company was incorporated in 1947 and is based in Mumbai, India."}}